Truck Scales / Weighbridges and DimensioningDimensioning, Weighing and Identification / Truck Scales and WeighbridgesHow can we assist you?►Expertise Library ►Product Finder ►Service Finder  We are the Leading Supplier for Transportation and Logistics Solutions WorldwideRugged and reliable truck scales are critical for weighing bulk goods bought or sold by the truckload. Truck scales are industrial scales that are capable of weighing trucks of all sizes. Often, they are used to monitor intake and output volumes at facilities, such as solid waste processing and recycling centers, construction sites and more. The truck scale consists of the foundation, which may be a permanent installation made from concrete; a truck scale or scale deck; the load cells, which are the sensors that measure the weighing on the scale; the terminal or indicator, which displays the weight value; and cables, which connect the load cells to the terminals. Legal-for-trade applications require scale calibration at certain intervals, which are determined by local weights and measures authorities. Truck scales can lose their accuracy over time, which is why regular calibration service is critical. Find guides, webinars and white papers about truck scales here. ProductsApplications PublicationsServicesMore InformationProductsApplications PublicationsServicesMore Information
Weighbridge Solutions and Truck Scales Products and solutions from the global leader in truck scales/weighbridges and load cells. Pallet and Parcel Dimensioners Automatic dimensioning of parcels and pallets for revenue recovery Dynamic Parcel Weighing High-speed, accurate weighing of parcels in motion. A wide variety of configurations and options facilitates easy integration into any material handling environment. Rail Scales Designed for easy and accurate weighing of rail cars to speed up throughput without compromising safety. Postal Scales  Ensuring accurate measurements and greater efficiency in postal applications. Forklift Scales These scales save time and money by enabling forklift trucks to weigh loads accurately. Pallet Jack Scales The BTA231 Pallet Truck Scale is a rugged and cost-effective solution and features a dependable terminal including a large, easily visible display and efficient keyboard. 






